{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "e5f6a7b8-c9d0-1234-ef01-345678901234",
    "name": "Lav60 - Listar Lojas",
    "description": "Collection para consultar **lojas cadastradas** no sistema.\n\n## Fluxo recomendado\n\n1. Configure `base_url` e `x_token`.\n2. Execute **Listar Lojas** ou **Listar Lojas (ativas)**.\n3. Use o `code` retornado como `store_code` nos próximos passos (produtos, PIX, vendas).\n\nDocumentação: `docs/guides/listar-lojas.md`",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    {
      "key": "serverUrl",
      "value": "http://127.0.0.1:3100"
    },
    {
      "key": "x_token",
      "value": "SEU_X_TOKEN",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "store_status",
      "value": "active",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "storeCode",
      "value": "pb05"
    }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Listar Lojas",
      "event": [
        {
          "listen": "test",
          "script": {
            "type": "text/javascript",
            "exec": [
              "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
              "    const stores = pm.response.json().data ?? [];",
              "",
              "    pm.test('Lojas retornadas', function () {",
              "        pm.expect(stores).to.be.an('array');",
              "    });",
              "",
              "    console.log('\\n--- Lojas ---');",
              "    stores.slice(0, 20).forEach((s) => {",
              "        const a = s.attributes ?? {};",
              "        console.log(`[${a.code}] ${a.name} — ${a.city}/${a.state} (${a.status})`);",
              "    });",
              "    if (stores.length > 20) console.log(`... e mais ${stores.length - 20} lojas`);",
              "",
              "    if (stores[0]?.attributes?.code) {",
              "        pm.collectionVariables.set('storeCode', stores[0].attributes.code);",
              "        console.log('\\nstoreCode salvo:', stores[0].attributes.code);",
              "    }",
              "    console.log('-------------\\n');",
              "}"
            ]
          }
        }
      ],
      "request": {
        "method": "GET",
        "header": [
          {
            "key": "X-Token",
            "value": "{{x_token}}"
          },
          {
            "key": "Accept",
            "value": "application/json"
          }
        ],
        "url": {
          "raw": "{{serverUrl}}/totem/api/v1/stores",
          "host": [
            "{{serverUrl}}/totem"
          ],
          "path": [
            "api",
            "v1",
            "stores"
          ]
        },
        "description": "Retorna todas as lojas ordenadas por código.\n\nSalva o primeiro `store_code` na variável da collection."
      },
      "response": []
    },
    {
      "name": "Listar Lojas (ativas)",
      "event": [
        {
          "listen": "test",
          "script": {
            "type": "text/javascript",
            "exec": [
              "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
              "    const stores = pm.response.json().data ?? [];",
              "    console.log('Lojas ativas:', stores.length);",
              "    if (stores[0]?.attributes?.code) {",
              "        pm.collectionVariables.set('storeCode', stores[0].attributes.code);",
              "    }",
              "}"
            ]
          }
        }
      ],
      "request": {
        "method": "GET",
        "header": [
          {
            "key": "X-Token",
            "value": "{{x_token}}"
          },
          {
            "key": "Accept",
            "value": "application/json"
          }
        ],
        "url": {
          "raw": "{{serverUrl}}/totem/api/v1/stores?status={{store_status}}",
          "host": [
            "{{serverUrl}}/totem"
          ],
          "path": [
            "api",
            "v1",
            "stores"
          ],
          "query": [
            {
              "key": "status",
              "value": "{{store_status}}",
              "description": "active | suspended | implantation | point | rental | paused | cancellation"
            }
          ]
        },
        "description": "Filtra lojas por status. Padrão: `active`."
      },
      "response": []
    }
  ]
}